# Report Format Specification

Canonical template for backtesto-agent reports. All generated reports MUST follow this structure.

> **Reference report**: See `docs/reports/test-portfolio-benchmark-2026-02-27.md` for a complete, validated example (60/60 PASS, includes benchmark).

## Non-Negotiable Rules

1. **Images complement tables — never replace them.** Every chart with extractable numeric data MUST have a corresponding markdown table. Images-only sections are acceptable ONLY for purely visual charts (portfolio value time series, rolling returns, drawdown timeline, return distribution, Monte Carlo).
2. **Composition tables use emoji flags/icons** (country flags, currency symbols, sector icons).
3. **All Plotly charts exported via DPR-override technique** at 1400×500 (wide) or 700×500 (half-width).

## Image Filename Convention

```
[PORTFOLIO]-[YYYY-MM-DD]-[chart-name].png
```

- Use tickers in filenames (e.g., `VWCE-EXUS-EIMI-2026-02-25-yearly.png`)
- Use abbreviated names/tickers in table cells (e.g., "VWCE", "EXUS")

## Section Order

### 1. Title + Date + Source

```markdown
# Backtest Report: [weights with tickers, e.g. "20% VWCE / 50% EXUS / 30% EIMI"]
**Date**: YYYY-MM-DD
**Source**: [backtes.to](https://backtes.to/)
```

### 2. Portfolio Allocation

```markdown
## Portfolio Allocation
| Asset | ISIN | Weight |
|-------|------|--------|
| VWCE | IE00BK5BQT80 | 20% |
| EXUS | IE00BD45YS76 | 50% |
| EIMI | IE00BKM4GZ66 | 30% |
```

### 3. Settings

Always include all four fields. Use "none" or "N/A" if not applicable.

```markdown
## Settings
- **Period**: MM/YYYY – MM/YYYY (or "max available")
- **Initial investment**: EUR X,XXX
- **Recurring**: EUR XXX/month (or "none")
- **Rebalancing**: [strategy] (or "none")
```

### 4. Performance Summary

Extended metrics table — include all available metrics from the Riassunto tab.

```markdown
## Performance Summary
| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| CAGR (Rendimento Annuale) | X.X% |
| Volatility | X.X% |
| Sharpe Ratio | X.XX |
| Max Drawdown | -X.X% |
| Average Drawdown | -X.X% |
| Max Drawdown Duration | X.X years |
| Ulcer Index | X.XX% |
```

### 5. Summary Chart

Screenshot from the Riassunto tab (donut allocation + summary). Image-only is acceptable here.

```markdown
## Summary
![Summary](images/[PORTFOLIO]-[DATE]-summary.png)
```

### 6. Performance Chart

Portfolio value over time. Image-only is acceptable (time series).

```markdown
## Portfolio Value
![Portfolio Value](images/[PORTFOLIO]-[DATE]-portfolio-value.png)
```

### 7. Yearly Returns Chart + Three-Column Table

Chart image FIRST, then compact three-column table.

```markdown
## Yearly Returns
![Yearly Returns](images/[PORTFOLIO]-[DATE]-yearly.png)

| Year | Return | Year | Return | Year | Return |
|------|--------|------|--------|------|--------|
| 2003 | +0.4% | 2011 | -10.9% | 2019 | +23.9% |
| 2004 | +12.3% | 2012 | +14.7% | 2020 | +3.0% |
| ...  | ...    | ...  | ...    | ...  | ...    |
```

Use `+` prefix for positive returns, `-` for negative. Fill columns top-to-bottom, left-to-right.

### 8. Risk Analysis Chart

Image-only (visual probability/loss charts).

```markdown
## Risk Analysis
![Max Loss](images/[PORTFOLIO]-[DATE]-max-loss.png)
![Success Probability](images/[PORTFOLIO]-[DATE]-loss-prob.png)
```

### 9. Drawdown Analysis Chart

Image-only (drawdown timeline).

```markdown
## Drawdown Analysis
![Drawdown](images/[PORTFOLIO]-[DATE]-drawdown.png)
```

### 10. Top 10 Holdings

Table FIRST, then chart image.

```markdown
## Top 10 Holdings

| Holding | Weight |
|---------|--------|
| Taiwan Semiconductor | 4.6% |
| Tencent Holdings | 2.2% |
| ... | ... |

![Top Holdings](images/[PORTFOLIO]-[DATE]-top-holdings.png)
```

